upto 5 read replicas
within az,cross az or cross region 

asynchronous replication happens in read replicas(eventually consistent)
replicas can be promoted to their own db

read replicas are used for only select kind of statements ex:read


rds multi az is used for disaster recovery:
rds db in another az happens synchronously

both has one dns name-so automatic failover to standby

read replicas can be set multi az for disaster recovery 
